      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. This car has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered more than my own kids! It\u2019s in truly stunning shape\u2014the kind of find that makes you do a double-take. The paint has that deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is just pristine. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth and responsive. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously cared for every single mile, this is the one. Come on by, have a chat, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of something special!",
