      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a turn-key enthusiast build maintained to a standard that surpasses factory tolerances. This specimen features a high-revving DOHC power plant with a perfectly linear torque curve and a zero-leak down-compression profile across all cylinders. The drivetrain is anchored by a high-bias limited-slip differential and a short-throw linkage for surgical gear engagement. We have refined the suspension geometry to maximize mechanical grip, utilizing adjustable damping rates that virtually eliminate body roll while maintaining absolute chassis composure. The undercarriage remains bone-dry, and the exterior has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating to preserve the factory paint depth. This is a mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the driver who demands peak performance and zero compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
